sec.p:
The ATLAS Collaboration uses various algorithms to identify
				b- and
				c-jets [
				5], referred to as flavour-tagging algorithms, when analysing data from
				pp collisions recorded during Run 2 of the LHC (2015â€“2018) at





									s

								=
								13


						\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
