The level of correlation between the different low-level algorithm outputs varies as a function of the jet flavour and the kinematic range. In general, large correlations between the IP2D, IP3D, SV1 and JetFitter algorithms are observed for heavy-flavour jets. However, these correlations are significantly reduced in the case of light-flavour jets. In addition, such correlations are further reduced in high-




